verbose_text: Calcipotriol (10 muM) shifted the distribution of embryos with increased runx1 / cmyb expression in a manner phenotypically comparable with 1,25 (OH) D3 (XREF_FIG) and caused a 29% elevation in Flk1 + cMyb + HSPCs (p < 0.05) by FACS (XREF_FIG).
evidence: caused a 29% elevation in Flk1 + cMyb +  HSPCs (p < 0.05) by FACS
